<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَعَبْدُ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنُ مَهْدِيٍّ وَإِسْحَاقُ وَأَبُو عُبَيْدٍ وَأَبُو ثَوْرٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَيَرَى الْحَنَفِيَّةُ وَعَطَاءٌ وَالزُّهْرِيُّ وَابْنُ شُبْرُمَةَ أَنَّ مَنْ أَعْسَر بِنَفَقَةِ امْرَأَتِهِ لَمْ يُفَرَّقْ بَيْنَهُمَا،<span class="c5"> وَيُقَال لَهَا:</span> اسْتَدِينِي.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلِمَعْرِفَةِ أَحْكَامِ الْفُرْقَةِ بِسَبَبِ ضَرَرِ فَقْدِ الزَّوْجِ أَوْ غَيْبَتِهِ <span class="c2">(ر: مَفْقُودٌ، غَيْبَةٌ، وَفَسْخٌ، وَطَلاَقٌ)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>ضَرَّةٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> قَسْمٌ بَيْنَ الزَّوْجَاتِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>ضِرْسٌ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
